			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi Phil,
<br />

<br />
I think everything is in order. After an user answered a question, the tool remembers it and doesn't bother the user anymore. It's a small usability trick to make your visitors happy.
<br />

<br />
If you want to see the question-answer form once again, you can: 1) change questions, or 2) clear browser cookies for the site.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
